		<lb n="13" break="no"/>ṟ cemmai <hi rend="grantha">A</hi>ṟupatiṉ kaḻañcu
	</p>

	<p>
		<unclear>Ip</unclear>
		<lb n="14" break="no"/>-poṉṉuḷ tāṉ piṟanta cōti-<unclear>nā</unclear>ḷ
